Computational Reproducibility

Authors table

Extracted from Table5â¦R file.

Original code listed many more libraries, but did not use them.

Code 
requireNamespace("stargazer")
Loading required namespace: stargazer
Code 
requireNamespace("lfe")
Loading required namespace: lfe

Modfied to reference functions through namespace, rather than load all libraries, and to reference data through path, rather than to change wd. Changed output of stargazer to plain text so it is included in report automatically.

Code 
data.dir <- "authors_replication/HuD_Replication/Final Data Sets/"

## Housing Search  ######################################################################################################

#Preamble

# Unless Otherwise Specified, Model Sequence is as follows:
# Model 1: treatment effect conditional on advertisement price
# Model 2: treatment effect also conditional on level of treatment outcome in advertised listing
# Model 3: treatment effect also conditional on racial composition of block group of advertised listing
# Model 4: treatment effect also conditional on racial composition of block group of recommended listing
# Model 5: treatment effect also conditional on price of recommended home

# Load data  

recs_trial_final <- readRDS(file.path(data.dir,"adsprocessed_JPE.rds"))

#construct separate indicators for market and control

recs_trial_final$market <- as.factor(sapply(strsplit(as.character(recs_trial_final$CONTROL), "-"), `[`, 1))
recs_trial_final$CONTROL <- as.factor(recs_trial_final$CONTROL)

recs_trial_final$show <- recs_trial_final$STOTUNIT
recs_trial_final$show[recs_trial_final$STOTUNIT<0] <- NA

#construct indicators for race groups
recs_trial_final$ofcolor <- 0
recs_trial_final$ofcolor[recs_trial_final$APRACE==2] <- 1
recs_trial_final$ofcolor[recs_trial_final$APRACE==3] <- 1
recs_trial_final$ofcolor[recs_trial_final$APRACE==4] <- 1
recs_trial_final$ofcolor <- as.factor(recs_trial_final$ofcolor)

recs_trial_final$count=1


# Dicrimination and Showings
# STEERING AND white NEIGHBORHOOD 

SHOW1 <- lfe::felm(show ~ ofcolor | CONTROL + SEQUENCE.x + month + HCITY + market + ARELATE2 + HHMTYPE + SAPPTAM + TSEX.x + THHEGAI + TPEGAI + THIGHEDU + TCURTENR +  ALGNCUR + AELNG1 + DPMTEXP + AMOVERS + age + ALEASETP + ACAROWN| 0 | CONTROL, data  = recs_trial_final)
SHOW3 <- lfe:: felm(show ~ ofcolor + w2012pc_Ad + b2012pc_Ad + a2012pc_Ad + hisp2012pc_Ad + logAdPrice | CONTROL + SEQUENCE.x + month + HCITY + market + ARELATE2 + HHMTYPE + SAPPTAM + TSEX.x + THHEGAI + TPEGAI + THIGHEDU + TCURTENR +  ALGNCUR + AELNG1 + DPMTEXP + AMOVERS + age + ALEASETP + ACAROWN| 0 |CONTROL, data  = recs_trial_final)

SHOW1_ <- lfe::felm(show ~ APRACE | CONTROL + SEQUENCE.x + month + HCITY + market + ARELATE2 + HHMTYPE + SAPPTAM + TSEX.x + THHEGAI + TPEGAI + THIGHEDU + TCURTENR +  ALGNCUR + AELNG1 + DPMTEXP + AMOVERS + age + ALEASETP + ACAROWN| 0 | CONTROL, data  = recs_trial_final)
SHOW3_ <- lfe::felm(show ~ APRACE + w2012pc_Ad + b2012pc_Ad + a2012pc_Ad + hisp2012pc_Ad + logAdPrice | CONTROL + SEQUENCE.x + month + HCITY + market + ARELATE2 + HHMTYPE + SAPPTAM + TSEX.x + THHEGAI + TPEGAI + THIGHEDU + TCURTENR +  ALGNCUR + AELNG1 + DPMTEXP + AMOVERS + age + ALEASETP + ACAROWN| 0 |CONTROL, data  = recs_trial_final)


##########################################################################################################################################################################

# STEERING 

recs_trial_final$home_av <- recs_trial_final$SAVLBAD
recs_trial_final$home_av[recs_trial_final$home_av<0] <- NA
recs_trial_final$home_av[recs_trial_final$home_av>1] <- 0

SHOWad1 <- lfe::felm(home_av ~ ofcolor | CONTROL + SEQUENCE.x + month + HCITY + market + ARELATE2 + HHMTYPE + SAPPTAM + TSEX.x + THHEGAI + TPEGAI + THIGHEDU + TCURTENR +  ALGNCUR + AELNG1 + DPMTEXP + AMOVERS + age + ALEASETP + ACAROWN| 0 | CONTROL, data  = recs_trial_final)
SHOWad3 <- lfe::felm(home_av ~ ofcolor + w2012pc_Ad + b2012pc_Ad + a2012pc_Ad + hisp2012pc_Ad + logAdPrice | CONTROL + SEQUENCE.x + month + HCITY + market + ARELATE2 + HHMTYPE + SAPPTAM + TSEX.x + THHEGAI + TPEGAI + THIGHEDU + TCURTENR +  ALGNCUR + AELNG1 + DPMTEXP + AMOVERS + age + ALEASETP + ACAROWN| 0 |CONTROL, data  = recs_trial_final)

SHOWad1_ <- lfe::felm(home_av ~ APRACE | CONTROL + SEQUENCE.x + month + HCITY + market + ARELATE2 + HHMTYPE + SAPPTAM + TSEX.x + THHEGAI + TPEGAI + THIGHEDU + TCURTENR +  ALGNCUR + AELNG1 + DPMTEXP + AMOVERS + age + ALEASETP + ACAROWN| 0 | CONTROL, data  = recs_trial_final)
SHOWad3_ <- lfe::felm(home_av ~ APRACE + w2012pc_Ad + b2012pc_Ad + a2012pc_Ad + hisp2012pc_Ad + logAdPrice | CONTROL + SEQUENCE.x + month + HCITY + market + ARELATE2 + HHMTYPE + SAPPTAM + TSEX.x + THHEGAI + TPEGAI + THIGHEDU + TCURTENR +  ALGNCUR + AELNG1 + DPMTEXP + AMOVERS + age + ALEASETP + ACAROWN| 0 |CONTROL, data  = recs_trial_final)

### GENERATE TABLES
out <- "tmp/"

###########Control Group Mean####################

stargazer::stargazer(SHOW1, SHOW3, SHOWad1, SHOWad3,
          type = "text",
          out = paste0(out, "HUM_tab5_JPE.r"),
          title="Steering and Neighborhood Effects",
          model.numbers = F,
          keep = c("ofcolor"),
          covariate.labels = c("Racial Minority"),
          keep.stat=c("n","adj.rsq"),
          digits=4,digits.extra=0,no.space=T,align=T,model.names=F,notes.append=T,object.names=F,
          add.lines = list(c("ln(Price) Advert Home","N","Y","N","Y"),
                           c("Racial Comp Advert Home","N","Y","N","Y")))

Steering and Neighborhood Effects

                        -----------------------------------

Code 
stargazer::stargazer(SHOW1_, SHOW3_, SHOWad1_, SHOWad3_,
          type = "text",
          out = paste0(out, "HUM_tab5_JPE_.txt"),
          title="Steering and Neighborhood Effects",
          dep.var.labels.include = F,
          column.labels = c("Number of Recommendations","Home Availability"),
          model.numbers = F,
          keep = c("APRACE"),
          covariate.labels = c("African American",
                               "Hispanic",
                               "Asian",
                               "Other"),
          keep.stat=c("n","adj.rsq"),
          digits=4,digits.extra=0,no.space=T,align=T,model.names=F,notes.append=T,object.names=F,
          add.lines = list(c("ln(Price) Advert Home","N","Y","N","Y"),
                           c("Racial Comp Advert Home","N","Y","N","Y")))

# Computational Reproducibility

Authors table![](figs/table5_orig.png)

Extracted from Table5...R file.

Original code listed many more libraries, but did not use them.

```{r setup}
requireNamespace("stargazer")
requireNamespace("lfe")
```

Modfied to reference functions through namespace, rather than load all libraries, and to reference data through path, rather than to change wd. Changed output of stargazer to plain text so it is included in report automatically.

